Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Shadow detection fails

Adjust threshold values in detect_shadows() method
Try different color spaces (HSV, LAB)
Ensure image has sufficient contrast
Issue: Inaccurate sun position calculations

Verify latitude/longitude coordinates are correct
Check timezone matches location
Ensure datetime is timezone-aware
Issue: No timestamp candidates found

Expand date range for search
Increase angle/elevation tolerance values
Verify shadow measurements are accurate
Issue: OpenCV display issues

Check X11 forwarding if using SSH
Use cv2.imwrite() to save instead of display
Verify OpenCV installation: python3 -c "import cv2; print(cv2.__version__)"
